{"tid":1006875,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華承諾補償不退票粉絲 「我一定會用我個人的方法去補償不想退票的朋友！」","createTime":"2019-02-03T10:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T17:26:48.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"990a4ad9d046134bc15d244824ed243f45d6eb57","tid":1006875,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"劉德華去年12月舉行一連20場的《My Love Andy Lau劉德華World Tour》跨年演唱會，由於不幸患上流感，無奈宣布取消 2018年12月28日至 2019年1月3日共七場的演唱會。其後主辦機構宣布向紅館申請今年12月的補場演出，結果未獲批。雖然演唱會主辦方早前已公布退款方法，不過華仔前晚再度於《華仔天地》官方網站的「我的心聲」中發文，向觀眾訴說對退票事宜的感受，指一定會用個人的方法去補償不想退票的朋友，引來不少粉絲力撐不會退票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wyswHy_ezXD3L3Sd0X6w4A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02b_enp01p01030219copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwyswHy_ezXD3L3Sd0X6w4A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02b_enp01p01030219copy.jpg&h=f92a8a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華仔承諾向不想退票的觀眾作出補償。<br />\n<br />\n華仔留言說：「在安排退票事宜的過程中， 發現原來主辦單位和各方機構中間牽涉的繁複， 實在是我意料之外。 在沒有選擇下， 這個月內只好耐心等候主辦單位和各機構達成協議， 統一退票安排方案。 現在也是時候向大家說一下， 首先感謝受影響觀眾的忍耐。 請信任我、所有退票、不退票的大家，都是我的朋友！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yEJtM7dw4MbBnP7b0RIAPA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D02b_enp01p03030219copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyEJtM7dw4MbBnP7b0RIAPA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD02b_enp01p03030219copy.jpg&h=e0230ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華仔發文感謝受影響觀眾的信任。<br />\n<br />\n「還有聽到部分朋友的聲音是希望我能以補場方式去安排， 這是我明白和理解的！補場的安排、中間存在太多我個人力量不能解決的難題， 所以我不能代表其他單位回應。 但是，我可以用個人的名義去答應不想退票的朋友， 請把你手上的票保存好，待退票流程完成之後， 我一定會用我個人的方法去補償不想退票的朋友！再說一次，所有退票、不退票的，都是我的朋友！所以退票的朋友務必將所有退票資料存檔， 日後也必然有辦法去照顧到你們！感謝！！新年快樂 身體健康！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/EFNjPQzSYY4U1u1q4onJLw--~B/aD01NzA7dz00NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20140706ap11y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEFNjPQzSYY4U1u1q4onJLw--~B%2FaD01NzA7dz00NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20140706ap11y.jpg&h=1f9948af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華仔因患上流感，取消了七場演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n有粉絲留言力撐華仔：「在心中從來沒有想過要退票！留 做紀念永遠支持你！」、「華仔，撐你，我選擇不退票。」"},{"pid":"bcf63daafc915c0efd373caf887b1ad4093ea75c","tid":1006875,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"黃牛又贏"},{"pid":"e0e50e735c25cdfd81d51440ff37975fb1049e91","tid":1006875,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78be9ca4c9a2d60ccc4d42f64bd8cafbd53eb48f","tid":1006875,"uid":56999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"今時今日<br />\n咁嘅服務 係唔撚夠㗎<br />\n<br />\n華仔你返去填海把啦"},{"pid":"982f223d0690b2b130884bd62c93ccaaef76a6b0","tid":1006875,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c98552654c456890badc734476241a7ebcdac9b","tid":1006875,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"填海囉，填個劉德華島出嚟"},{"pid":"9468b418508b8b090e0ec113f2e5d700d2dfde3c","tid":1006875,"uid":100017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"點解有長毛張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf0632b2dd12baeea0b1a54a1d50262ecbbfcc0","tid":1006875,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":